 of the value in the `Dynamic` determines how it is interpreted\nand rendered.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Extension.html#Lean.ElabInline.custom","kind":"ctor","line":35,"name":"Lean.ElabInline.custom","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/DocString/Extension.lean#L35-L39"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Extension.html#Lean.ElabInline\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">ElabInline</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Saved data that describes a custom inline element.\n\nThe type of value contained within the `Dynamic` determines the interpretation of the custom\nelement, including how it is rendered to Markdown for the language server.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Extension.html#Lean.ElabInline","kind":"inductive","line":28,"name":"Lean.ElabInline","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/DocString/Extension.lean#L28-L46"}}],"imports":["Init.Data.String.Extra","Init.Data.String.Length","Init.Data.String.Search","Init.Data.String.TakeDrop","Init.Omega","Lean.DeclarationRange","Lean.DocString.DeferredCheck","Lean.DocString.Types"],"instances":[{"className":"Repr","name":"Lean.instReprElabInline","typeNames":["Lean.ElabInline"]},{"className":"Repr","name":"Lean.instReprElabBlock","typeNames":["Lean.ElabBlock"]},{"className":"Inhabited","name":"Lean.instInhabitedVersoDocString","typeNames":["Lean.VersoDocString"]},{"className":"Inhabited","name":"Lean.VersoModuleDocs.instInhabitedSnippet","typeNames":["Lean.VersoModuleDocs.Snippet"]},{"className":"Repr","name":"Lean.VersoModuleDocs.instReprSnippet","typeNames":["Lean.VersoModuleDocs.Snippet"]},{"className":"Inhabited","name":"Le